# Enterprise-Grade Dashboard UI/UX Refactoring

Elevate the Airawata dashboard from its current "Claymorphism / earth-tone" aesthetic to an ultra-minimalist, enterprise-grade application following strict functional design principles.

## Audit Summary — Current Issues

| Problem | Where | Violation |
|---|---|---|
| Heavy claymorphism shadows (`clay-card`, `clay-btn`, `clay-input`) | `globals.css` L190-380 | Anti-AI cliché: heavy shadows, backdrop-blur, clay 3D |
| Floating blob animations (`clay-float-1/2/3`, `clay-blob`) | `globals.css` L382-477 | Anti-AI cliché: floating 3D geometric blobs |
| Earth-tone gradient backgrounds on cards | `highlight-card.tsx`, dashboards | Anti-AI cliché: complex gradients |
| `2rem` border-radius on cards, `rounded-full` on inputs | Multiple components | Over-rounded corners (pill-shaped) |
| Decorative serif heading font (Playfair Display) | `layout.tsx` | Not a geometric/neo-grotesque system font |
| `shadow-earth-lg`, `shadow-earth-sm` utilities | `globals.css` | Forbidden heavy drop-shadows |
| `backdrop-blur-md` on header | `header.tsx` | Glassmorphism |
| Inconsistent spacing (mix of `p-5`, `p-6`, `p-8`, `gap-4`, `gap-6`, `gap-8`) | All components | No 8pt grid discipline |
| Saturated rose/emerald/amber/indigo gradients on cards | Role dashboards | Not monochromatic/low-saturation |
| `hover:scale-[1.02]`, `hover:-translate-y-1`, `transform` animations | Member/Peneliti dashboards | Dramatic scaling on hover |
| `Playfair_Display` + `Plus_Jakarta_Sans` dual-font | Root layout | Serif heading doesn't match minimalist spec |

