## Design Token System (New)

### Color Palette — Strict Monochromatic

```
--background:       #FFFFFF    (Pure white)
--surface:          #FAFAFA    (Off-white, for sidebar/cards)
--foreground:       #111111    (Near-black, primary text)
--text-secondary:   #6B7280    (gray-500, secondary text)
--text-tertiary:    #9CA3AF    (gray-400, tertiary/placeholder)
--border:           rgba(0,0,0,0.08)   (Ultra-subtle border)
--border-strong:    rgba(0,0,0,0.12)   (Slightly more visible)
--accent:           #4F46E5    (Indigo-600, single muted accent)
--accent-light:     #EEF2FF    (Indigo-50, accent background)
--destructive:      #DC2626    (Red-600, unchanged for semantics)
--success:          #16A34A    (Green-600)
--warning:          #D97706    (Amber-600)
```

### Typography — Inter (Neo-Grotesque)

| Role | Size | Weight | Letter-spacing | Line-height |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Page title (h1) | 24px (1.5rem) | 600 | -0.025em | 1.2 |
| Section title (h2) | 18px (1.125rem) | 600 | -0.01em | 1.3 |
| Widget title (h3) | 14px (0.875rem) | 600 | 0 | 1.4 |
| Body | 14px (0.875rem) | 400 | 0 | 1.5 |
| Small / Meta | 12px (0.75rem) | 500 | 0.01em | 1.5 |
| Label / Overline | 11px (0.6875rem) | 600 | 0.05em | 1 |

### Spacing — 8pt Grid

All margins, paddings, gaps derive from multiples of 8px:
`4px (0.25rem)` half-step for micro, `8px`, `16px`, `24px`, `32px`, `40px`, `48px`

### Borders & Radii

- Radius: `2px` (sharp) to `6px` (max)
- Border: `1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08)`

